Known Bugs
----------

- Dragging keysframes in the animation editor will cause a few
  GLib errors and eventually a segfault

- The bifurcation diagrams only update when they are redrawn,
  such as when your mouse enters or leaves them.

- Errors in opening or saving files aren't reported properly

- The 'save' menu items actually are 'save as' for now

- There's no about box

- File dialogs don't remember their previous directory

- The AVI files exported by Fyre don't open in windows media player

